d" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1024" height="658" natural-width="1024" natural-height="658" style="" data-lg-size="2048x2048" loading="lazy"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1708699541832" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1708699541832"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With its revolutionary low-viscosity liquid gel ink, the Pentel EnerGel formula is smoother-flowing and quicker-drying than ordinary gel ink, giving a similar sensation to liquid ink. It's great for left-handers thanks to its fast-drying properties. Available in 12 different models with a range of ink colour variations.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div data-index="2" class="item-content"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675767519795" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1675767519795" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/collections/pentel-mattehop" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/32e0c890-c298-46e7-a91d-f22529392496/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/pentel-tile-001.jpg" alt="Pentel Mattehop" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1024" height="658" natural-width="1024" natural-height="658" style="" data-lg-size="2048x2048" loading="lazy"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770760680" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1675770760680"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>&nbsp;</p><p>A step up from a standard gel pen, the Pentel Mattehop offers brilliantly smooth, high opacity ink that gives  a matte, plastic finish when dry.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: transparent;">Also suitable for photographic and coated paper and works well as a drawing or colouring pen.&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">Available in a range of vibrant colours.</span></p></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div data-index="3" class="item-content"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1707754406815" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1707754406815" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/collections/pentel-sign-pens" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/ed65597c-5825-49ac-b8b2-0b763284af1d/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/pentel-tile-002.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1024" height="658" natural-width="1024" natural-height="658" style="" data-lg-size="2048x2048" loading="lazy"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1707754406745" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1707754406745"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Pentel Touch Brush Sign Pen SES15 is a version of the popular and long-lived Pentel Sign Pen, but with a brush tip.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: transparent;">The Touch Brush Sign Pen adds a further dimension to the popular Sign Pen, capable of expressive strokes with its flexible fibre tip. Non-permanent water-based ink.</span></p></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div data-index="4" class="item-content"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1707754408518" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1707754408518" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/collections/pentel-graphgear" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/13e446d9-2787-49f3-b853-2cbc161b1867/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/pentel-tile-005.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1024" height="658" natural-width="1024" natural-height="658" style="" data-lg-size="2048x2048" loading="lazy"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1707754408613" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1707754408613"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>A really nice heavy metal automatic pencil with a comfortable grip that's a mixture of knurled metal and translucent rubber. The metal lead sleeve retracts completely when you press down on the clip, to protect both the lead and sleeve. There's a lead hardness indicator, an integral refillable eraser under the chromed cap, and the pencil is available in 5 lead sizes.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div data-index="5" class="item-content"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1708704563852" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1708704563852" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/products/pentel-dual-metallic-brush-pen" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/4b93876b-9f42-42a6-bc37-2fe6d279f942/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/pentel-tile-003.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1024" height="658" natural-width="1024" natural-height="658" style="" data-lg-size="2048x2048" loading="lazy"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1708704563807" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1708704563807"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Pentel's Dual Metallic brush pens are something a bit different. Each pen gives you not one, but two different shades, and it doesn't involve flipping between twin tips. Shimmering metallic ink ensures that whether you're writing on black, white or coloured paper, two different shades will be apparent.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="gf-carousel-loading"><div class="gf-caousel-ripple"><div></div><div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1707754091749" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1707754091749"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1707754091722" data-id="1707754091722"><div data-label="Youtube" data-key="youtube" data-atomgroup="module" id="m-1708697723416" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-youtube" data-ver="1" data-id="1708697723416"><div class="module gf_module- " data-url="https://youtu.be/Y6ufOiMYEf0" data-width="" data-height="" data-responsive="1" data-sound="0" data-autoplay="1" data-loop="1" data-controls="1" data-showinfo="" data-modestbranding="0" data-fs="1" data-rel="" data-hd="" data-start="" data-end=""></div><div class="gf_youtube-overlay"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1708944684797" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1708944684797"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><font color="#000000"><a href="/products/pentel-colour-brush-pen-gfl" class="">The Pentel Colour Brush Pen</a> is a premium quality, nylon tip brush pen available in a range of 24 beautiful vivid translucent colours.</font></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><font color="#000000">Valve-activated for smooth flow, without leaking the synthetic fibre tip retains its shape.</font></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><font color="#000000">Excellent for wet-on-wet techniques as demonstrated here by <a href="https://www.blinklettering.co.uk" class="">Milly from Blink Lettering</a>.</font></p></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><script>window.__gemStoreData = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid.bestWayAddToCart = 1;</script></div><div id="divContentBk"></div><!--End_Gem_Page_Main_Editor-->
